<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_4826f314-5410-42ac-8a99-dffd867cc687" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10b"/></meta><sptc>10.2.16</sptc><title id="_8bf4057d-aa28-4132-8a7c-aeab7bbdc313">Hob construction</title><archive-num>New for 2022</archive-num><subclause id="_4caee0d0-90a5-4136-a7ad-9075eee82ecc" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_4dc81a17-d920-4ca7-9b9c-7e8977658c4e">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/4660_0.4.0.xml#_6daa7d7f-9147-4c10-98bc-c3cee9774bdb" id="_954fc36c-c986-4dff-8e75-3dcd3f711c15" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Hobs</xref> must be constructed of—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_44c99aee-82f5-441f-937b-228d51ef80ed">masonry; or</li><li id="_4598b225-01fa-4a86-bf40-44cd70f1f563">concrete; or</li><li id="_c65b52ea-a39b-4209-aae3-8fae07fd3990">autoclaved aerated concrete; or</li><li id="_a80ec8f9-b052-4301-8324-28c92a25aadd">extruded polyurethane foam,</li></ol><p>in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/4922_0.15.0.xml#_2dfcf7e9-a931-4f1e-b3f9-078a21418fd6" id="_936a0af3-ecb0-4638-a841-90b3b72e3063" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">Figure 10.2.16</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_188d816a-2642-4077-8fa7-2069c72a2938" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_dd385e97-4e1d-48a1-9817-e17fbf64c53c">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>All gaps, joints and intersections of the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/4660_0.4.0.xml#_6daa7d7f-9147-4c10-98bc-c3cee9774bdb" id="_f1a17022-565f-4e2c-a051-e50714eb7d57" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">hob</xref> substrate must be made flush before application of a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/4651_0.4.0.xml#_6e2c1aaa-5993-4850-908f-ac4007e94535" id="_5e65e435-d7e2-491e-9042-a05be488dfba" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">membrane</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_5c1ed37e-b632-460b-83ef-7a25d1590baf" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_17cf3a33-b4f8-4f68-b15a-01df950b35cb">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p><xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/4660_0.4.0.xml#_6daa7d7f-9147-4c10-98bc-c3cee9774bdb" id="_7ed2a0c0-64a8-4a06-95d1-d8dcd13a5b0d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Hobs</xref> must be adequately secured to the floor and sealed against the wall prior to applying a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/4651_0.4.0.xml#_6e2c1aaa-5993-4850-908f-ac4007e94535" id="_f3b5393f-fda4-4e8f-b3e5-ee6d76d607a3" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">membrane</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_df96a2b2-7e6a-485b-ab6a-b580195c187c" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_e335cb8f-5d0c-4813-84a9-893b714f7c3b">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>Timber must not be used for <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/4660_0.4.0.xml#_6daa7d7f-9147-4c10-98bc-c3cee9774bdb" id="_323df7bc-354e-43a3-af59-364d9f20c68b" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">hob</xref> construction.</p></subclause><image-reference author="Kieran O'Donnell" conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/2abe2d62-a871-4509-969b-2425466626a4/4922_0.15.0.xml" dateTime="2021-03-18T17:53:11" id="_2dfcf7e9-a931-4f1e-b3f9-078a21418fd6" type="insert"><num/><title id="_bdee5dae-3a74-4a23-ac83-6bbabf4edd20"/></image-reference></clause>